<h2 id="running-a-bitcoin-full-node"><a href="https://www.lopp.net/bitcoin-information/full-node.html">Running a Bitcoin Full Node</a></h2>

<blockquote>
  <p>While managing your own keys ensures that you can‚Äôt lose your money due to the negligence or maliciousness of a custodian, running a full node ensures that you can‚Äôt be tricked into accepting invalid bitcoin payments. Running and using your own node gives you the strongest security model Bitcoin has to offer.</p>
</blockquote>

<ul>
  <li><a href="https://blog.lopp.net/securing-your-financial-sovereignty/">Why Run a Full Node?</a></li>
